data.title: Australian Off-Road Caravans & Campers Manufacturer
data.meta_description: TEKTON EXPEDITION VEHICLES - The Home Of Class Leading Design, Innovation & Manufacturing - Enabling Your Journey To Escape The Ordinary and Explore The Extraordinary... One Track At A Time.
data.text:
The Tekton has been designed with elegance and purpose.

Making it extremely aerodynamic.

It's unique design not only looks great, but leads to greater fuel economy.

Applying our innovative & exclusive proprietary design.

We have reduced the trailers overall footprint, without compromise on internal size, with an extended A-Frame.

The Tekton is 2ft smaller overall then its competitors, with the same sized body.

The Tekton has not only been designed & engineered above Australian regulations & standards.

But has done extensive real world R&D testing across the entire continent, in some of the most extreme & harshest, climates & terrain.

​

The Tekton XT-3 has been built with purpose. Aerodynamically designed, to sit behind your tow vehicle with minimal drag.

Aggressive approach and departure angles, enhances the XT-3's off-road capabilities. Featuring a rear external kitchen and internal sleeping.

The XT-3 has been designed to go anywhere.

The SVX-4, is in a class of its own.

Uncompromising on all aspects of an expedition vehicle. Aerodynamic & compact design, with complete functionality.

​

The SVX-4 has been developed for true exploration.

The SVX-5, is a light weight, self contained, compact unit. With its aerodynamic body and narrow foot print, designed to follow your tow vehicle anywhere.

Without sacrificing the convenience of a luxury caravan, the SVX-5 is the perfect balance between camper and caravan.

Our innovation and passion stems from extensive years of travel in some of Australias most remote locations.

​

Our objective is to manufacture a light weight compact vehicle, with no sacrifice on structural integrity.

To reduce the trailers overall footprint without compromising on internal space.

Utilising our class leading innovation and exclusive proprietary design, we have been able to achieve this.

We have created an aerodynamic, compact, light weight and functional go anywhere expedition vehicle. Enhancing it's on and off-road capability and dynamics.

A vehicle without boundaries.

At Tekton we understand that one size doesn't fit all. That's why all our valued customers get to experience our Bespoke program when ordering a Tekton. For those who value uniqueness and embrace difference. Tekton presents a team of designers and engineers, starting with a blank sheet of paper, in collaboration with you, we can design & develop whatever you imagine your personal bespoke expedition vehicle to be (within limits). Every Tekton that leaves our facility are one of a kind.
